snippet.title: Touhou-Inspired Bullet Hell Game | Digital Soul Data Gameplay (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Digital Soul Data is a top-down bullet hell shooter which you play as a hacker, Mia, who uses avatar NB4 to blast her way through cyberspace and retrieve her sister's Digital Soul from eternal virtual slavery.

Like, Comment, and Subscribe if you like the video!
